{"tid":467032,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"［多圖］「異形飛蛾」多毛觸鬚超嚇人　大埔屯門友喊驚","createTime":"2017-11-13T06:32:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-13T18:11:13.000Z","uid":2547,"like":86,"dislike":25,"uniUserReply":57,"replies":[{"pid":"3f682d5094bcd4b1fceffa04f103019eb831eb0f","tid":467032,"uid":2547,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:32:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/142829_a60c9ecae325ac024739cbbf7ac11b17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F142829_a60c9ecae325ac024739cbbf7ac11b17.jpg&h=0f83ea17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/143118_80f5a918794dd8b100e6cc70d844f20c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F143118_80f5a918794dd8b100e6cc70d844f20c.jpg&h=11a85809&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/143122_55305e9e793dba0622cd8214a3bcd400.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F143122_55305e9e793dba0622cd8214a3bcd400.jpg&h=9234d026&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/143126_35e6fd8f81c0a9ced7baa03c0284bd0a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F13%2F143126_35e6fd8f81c0a9ced7baa03c0284bd0a.jpg&h=9c08e6e8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n蛾出沒請注意！早前一隻外表奇怪兼「核突」、貌似飛蛾的昆蟲照片在台灣瘋傳，該物種有橙紅色身軀、灰色翅膀，尾部還有4條毛茸茸、類似「觸鬚」的部位。照片流傳到香港後，不少平時飽受蛇蟲鼠蟻困擾的市民，包括大埔及屯門區的居民，紛紛留言表示非常擔心這奇怪生物會「入侵」住宅。而蛾類專家及香港鱗翅目學會創辦人之一的甘狄克（Roger Kendrick）博士則解釋，其「觸鬚」會釋放香氣吸引異性，對人類沒有害，呼籲市民遇到此類灰燈蛾時無需驚慌。<br />\n<br />\n野生生物顧問公司董事甘狄克，在港研究蛾類超過20年，他指照片中的蛾是黑條灰燈蛾（Creatonotos gangis），在中國南部及台灣可以找到，但香港暫未有發現。根據本港紀錄，曾出現兩種跟黑條灰燈蛾同為灰燈蛾屬（Creatonotos）的相近品種，分別是八點灰燈蛾（Creatonotos transiens）及暫無中文譯名的Creatonotos fasciatus。<br />\n<br />\n甘狄克又表示相中黑條灰燈蛾身後的「觸鬚」，其實是發香器（coremata），在每年的繁殖季節，雄蛾獨有的發香器就會鼓脹起來，並發出香氣吸引異性。翻查資料，原來一眾雄蛾會互相比較自己「雄偉」的發香器，而雌蛾就從中尋找交配對象。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/32.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好撚核突嘔心"},{"pid":"d6d74a51d521e059b84d08228bb6af4993dea69a","tid":467032,"uid":60578,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:34:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f512d835f7657f44bb8c81431b4e219ec7802d2","tid":467032,"uid":21423,"like":27,"dislike":94,"score":-67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:34:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ba5b6747a17adbac65d3fa70ceed9b1a5f917ddc","tid":467032,"uid":116530,"like":4,"dislike":68,"score":-64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:36:43.000Z","msg":"好靚喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6c93bae2214cd458187b569c0faf3b37302e6b6","tid":467032,"uid":146917,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"我鳩毛仲多過佢"},{"pid":"323913f8eb6ac4bd26a28c83ed530512b8684f85","tid":467032,"uid":2547,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:06:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"433674ebde438ae0e75758b2e45f368338f5025c","tid":467032,"uid":7840,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:08:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7857f1b0315d7ae334eef90b0fe70ffdc0509589","tid":467032,"uid":127611,"like":6,"dislike":42,"score":-36,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:11:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/13/142